snippet: As other senators working on a bipartisan overhaul expressed optimism, Senator Marco Rubio, Republican of Florida, issued a strongly worded message of caution.
abstract: Florida Republican Sen Marco Rubio issues a strongly worded message of caution as other senators work on a bipartisan overhaul of the nation's immigration laws; his aim is to keep expectations in check until details of the legislation are complete.
lead_paragraph: As other senators working on a bipartisan overhaul expressed optimism, Senator Marco Rubio, Republican of Florida, issued a strongly worded message of caution.

headline.seo: Rubio Offers Words of Caution on Immigration
headline.main: Rubio Says Immigration Bill Still Has a Way to Go
headline.print_headline: Rubio Says Immigration Bill Still Has a Way to Go
